{"id": 59549, "date": "2025-09-04T04:00:09", "date_gmt": "2025-09-04T11:00:09", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59549"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T10:39:11", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-24T17:39:11", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-4-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/04/kingdom-of-days-september-4-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 4"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>On a blustery night in Asbury Park, The Bruce Springsteen Band plays their second night of their residency at the Student Prince, while at the nearby Wonder Bar, Norman Seldin and the Joyful Noyze is in session. During an intermission at the Wonder Bar, new Joyful Noyze member Clarence Clemons walks over to the Student Prince to check out the talent. According to legend, the door blows off its hinges when Clarence opens it, leading to a memorable first meeting between Bruce and Clarence. <span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(Joyful Noyze photo credit: Billy Smith)</span></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4129\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-0904/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1971-0904.jpg?fit=679%2C535&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"679,535\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-0904\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1971-0904.jpg?fit=679%2C535&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4129 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1971-0904.jpg?resize=679%2C535&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"679\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1971-0904.jpg?w=679&amp;ssl=1 679w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1971-0904.jpg?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1972:\u00a0</strong>Bruce performs an early solo set on open-mic night at Max&#8217;s Kansas City in New York. Local musician David Blue catches Bruce&#8217;s performance and invites Bruce to zip downtown with him to catch his set with Jackson Browne at The Bitter End. David introduces Bruce to Jackson, convincing Jackson to let Bruce do an intermission set that night. Bruce plays for about an hour, the start of a career-long friendship with Jackson.</p>\n<p>Also on or about this night, Bonnie Raitt plays across the street at the Gaslight Au Go Go, and Bruce joins <em>her</em> on stage for a song as well.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce drops by Jackson Browne&#8217;s show at The Main Point in Bryn Mawr, Pennsylvania, where Bruce had performed an already legendary show earlier that year. Jackson invites Bruce on stage to perform an acoustic version of &#8220;Born to Run&#8221; and perhaps other songs as well.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4140\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0904/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0904.jpg?fit=658%2C730&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"658,730\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0904\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0904.jpg?fit=658%2C730&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4140 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0904.jpg?resize=658%2C730&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"658\" height=\"730\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0904.jpg?w=658&amp;ssl=1 658w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1975-0904.jpg?resize=270%2C300&amp;ssl=1 270w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and Steve make a guest appearance for &#8220;I Don&#8217;t Want to Go Home&#8221; and &#8220;Having a Party&#8221; with Southside Johnny and the Asbury Jukes at The Stone Pony.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WXSDFvmvpVA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Bruce is keeping busy on stage, because he&#8217;s unable to record. Billboard publishes an article today explaining Bruce&#8217;s legal predicament.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4144\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-0904/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?fit=494%2C501&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"494,501\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1431180780&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-0904\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?fit=494%2C501&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4144 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?resize=494%2C501&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"494\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?w=494&amp;ssl=1 494w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?resize=296%2C300&amp;ssl=1 296w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1976-0904.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 494px) 100vw, 494px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with The Shots, the new Stone Pony house band on &#8220;Farther Up the Road&#8221; and &#8220;Funky Broadway.&#8221;</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"VideoPress Video Player\" aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='569' src='https://videopress.com/embed/KXWUSmka?hd=0&amp;cover=1' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script src='https://v0.wordpress.com/js/next/videopress-iframe.js?m=1770107250'></script></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jp0sUB4Kc_Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Beaver Brown at Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank.</p>\n<div id=\"v-xxwmH9gZ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/xxwmH9gZ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their first of two nights at The Centrum in Worcester, Massachusetts.</p>\n<div id=\"v-RvNDhcgd-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/RvNDhcgd?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>Today is also the deadline for MTV&#8217;s &#8220;On the Road with Bruce Springsteen&#8221; contest, where fans can win an opportunity to join Bruce on tour for a week. Check out the commercial and imagine what it would have been like to win this contest:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XaCEUW0FNYA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>&#8230;and then check out the experience the winner actually had. MTV and Bruce more than lived up to their promise!</p>\n<div id=\"v-bXyEbWsI-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/bXyEbWsI?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"59555\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/04/kingdom-of-days-september-4-2/the_republican_1984_09_05_20/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?fit=980%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"980,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Republican_1984_09_05_20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?fit=392%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-59555 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1980&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1980\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?w=980&amp;ssl=1 980w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=115%2C300&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=392%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 392w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C2007&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=588%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 588w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/The_Republican_1984_09_05_20-scaled.jpg?resize=784%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 784w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29213\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-04a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?fit=1107%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1107,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598380981&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-09-04a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?fit=688%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29213 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?resize=758%2C1128&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1128\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?w=1107&amp;ssl=1 1107w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?resize=202%2C300&amp;ssl=1 202w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?resize=688%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 688w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?resize=768%2C1143&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-04a.jpg?resize=1032%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1032w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20887\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-04b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1984-09-04b.jpg?fit=728%2C1641&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"728,1641\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598381029&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;